    • Method Detail

      • load

        public SearchIndexerStateHolder load(SearchIndexerConfiguration indexerConfiguration)
        This method loads the SearchIndexerState.
        Please avoid multiple calls of this method for the same configuration as it is unspecified if the implementation will reload the state on each call.
        Specified by:
        load in interface SearchIndexerStateLoader
        Parameters:
        indexerConfiguration - is the SearchIndexerConfiguration. It will be used to create according the source-state objects and to determine the location where to load the state from.
        Returns:
        the loaded SearchIndexerState.
